<p>For halloween, Dima News Network has gotten a fresh look to celebrate.</p>
<p>Heres what the team has done for this years halloween!</p>

<h1>Homepage & Icons</h1>
<figure>
    <img src={{"images/Halloween-2025/homepage.png" | absolute_url }} alt="The homepage of Dima News Network, decorated for halloween 2025.">
    <figcaption>DNN Halloween Homepage</figcaption>
</figure>
<br>
<ul>
    <li>All of our official branding has gone from pink to orange!</li>
    <li>You may also notice a light orange gradient at the top of the home page. Looks pretty cool</li>
</ul>

<h1>Hammer Game</h1>

<p>If you didn't know, DNN has a easter egg on the coming soon page.</p>
<p>This page is accessed by going to the <code>More</code> or <code>Stories</code> sections.</p>

<br>
<p>You are able to click the hammer to begin a secret mini-game!</p>
    
<img src={{"images/Halloween-2025/image.png" | absolute_url }} alt="The DNN coming soon page.">

<p>Heres everything that was added to the hammer game for halloween:</p>

