<h2>New game-event...</h2>
<p>A new event has been added when you reach <strong><em>15,000</em></strong> score... Bloodmoon!</p>
<figure>
    <img src={{"images/Halloween-2025/bloodmoon-happening.png" | absolute_url }} alt="A screenshot of a bloodmoon occuring.">
    <figcaption>The bloodmoon.</figcaption>
</figure>

<br>
<p>During a bloodmoon, more difficult enemies will spawn more frequently. Quads will also begin spawning.</p>
<p>When a bloodmoon occurs, a new enemy also spawns...</p>

<div class="halloween-2025-enemy-cards">
    <div class="halloween-2025-enemy-redesign-card">
        <img src={{"assets/site-assets/hammer-enemies/bloodquad.png" | absolute_url }} class="pixelated-img">
        <div class="halloween-2025-enemy-info">
            <h1>Bloodquad</h1>
            <ul>
                <li>The bloodquad is a new enemy that spawns during the bloodmoon.</li>
                <li>Unlike a normal quad, it only takes 1 hit to kill.</li>
                <li>However, the bloodquad can move.</li>
                <li>It can move in:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Circles,</li>
                        <li>Waves,</li>
                        <li>or in Ovals.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Only 2 bloodquads can be alive at once.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h1>End</h1>
<p>That was everything that was added in the 2025 halloween update.</p>
<p>Maybe we'll do more of these for things like Christmas or next halloween.</p>
<br>
<p>Happy Halloween!</p>

